<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Episode 15]</i></font>

4
00:00:16,910 --> 00:00:18,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini lamaran
kakakku. Wang Jeon...</font>

5
00:00:19,550 --> 00:00:21,780
<font color=#FFFF00>...membawa surat lamaran ke
rumah Menteri Keuangan.</font>

6
00:00:23,790 --> 00:00:25,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hentikan dia.</font>

7
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:26,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau sungguh ingin menghentikannya?</font>

8
00:00:26,890 --> 00:00:28,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat menyedihkan.</font>

9
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:30,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa melakukan apapun.</font>

10
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:35,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hentikan dia, Jeoha.</font>

11
00:00:36,630 --> 00:00:38,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Aku mengerti.</font>

12
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus keluar.</font>

13
00:00:41,570 --> 00:00:42,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Jeoha.</font>

14
00:00:42,710 --> 00:00:44,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan siapkan banyak penjaga.</font>

15
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:47,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus terlihat seperti
Putra Mahkota.</font>

16
00:00:51,610 --> 00:00:52,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

17
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang Mulia telah mengizinkan...</font>

18
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:58,450
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernikahan ini.</font>

19
00:00:58,650 --> 00:01:00,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Menghentikan pernikahan ini berarti
anda membangkangnya.</font>

20
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:03,190
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku tahu.
- Dia pasti sangat marah.</font>

21
00:01:03,190 --> 00:01:05,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Lin juga tahu itu.</font>

22
00:01:05,630 --> 00:01:06,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa...</font>

23
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:09,330
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia berkeliaran selama...</font>

24
00:01:09,330 --> 00:01:11,700
<font color=#FFFF00>...enam hari ini, karena mencoba...</font>

25
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:14,770
<font color=#FFFF00>...menghentikan perkawinan itu dengan sendiri
sampai bibirnya menjadi pucat.</font>

26
00:01:15,810 --> 00:01:16,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah begitu, Lin?</font>

27
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:22,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau jangan ikut.
Kau nanti bisa dapat masalah.</font>

28
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:29,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang akan mengurus ini.</font>

29
00:01:47,570 --> 00:01:48,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu...</font>

30
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:51,440
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidaklah pantas bagiku untuk
menerobos masuk seperti ini.</font>

31
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:54,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada yang ingin anda katakan, Seja Jeoha?</font>

32
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:06,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus menghentikan lamaran hari ini...</font>

33
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:09,090
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan batalkan pernikahannya.</font>

34
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tahu...</font>

35
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:19,040
<font color=#FFFF00>...berapa banyak harta yang dimiliki oleh...</font>

36
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...Menteri Keuangan?</font>

37
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:23,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha, pernikahan
ini sudah...</font>

38
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:26,480
<font color=#FFFF00>...diizinkan oleh Yang Mulia.</font>

39
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:33,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memiliki 40.000 vila dengan
lahan pertanian di seluruh penjuru negeri,</font>

40
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:36,050
<font color=#FFFF00>10.500 kg biji-bijian yang dipanen
dari tanah itu setiap tahun,</font>

41
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,590
<font color=#FFFF00>2.500 pelayan di seluruh penjuru negeri,</font>

42
00:02:38,750 --> 00:02:41,160
<font color=#FFFF00>6 besi meteor, 5 armada,</font>

43
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan sekitar 20 kapal...</font>

44
00:02:44,990 --> 00:02:46,430
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan masing-masing armadanya.</font>

45
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:50,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah harta yang dimiliki
oleh Menteri Keuangan.</font>

46
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mencari tahunya dengan buru-buru,</font>

47
00:02:52,670 --> 00:02:55,040
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi kemungkinan masih ada yang
belum aku ketahui.</font>

48
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan ini harta...</font>

49
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:04,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang akan diberikan kepada
Wang Jeon setelah ia menikah.</font>

50
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:08,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dengar banyak harta yang akan
diserahkan setelah ia menikah.</font>

51
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:12,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Armada di Sungai Yeseong,</font>

52
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:14,460
<font color=#FFFF00>12 vila,</font>

53
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,490
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan 750 kg gandum.</font>

54
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:23,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau merasa diancam?</font>

55
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:28,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa hartamu itu belum cukup,</font>

56
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,040
<font color=#FFFF00>...Kanselir?</font>

57
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:33,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau tiba-tiba menjadi serakah?</font>

58
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:44,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jumlah tentara yang kau
latih di Gunung Yoam...</font>

59
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:50,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...pasti semakin banyak.</font>

60
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:53,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti membutuhkan uang untuk memberi mereka makan.</font>

61
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:54,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun,</font>

62
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau memerlukan banyak tentara?</font>

63
00:03:57,970 --> 00:04:01,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengerti mengapa anda mengatakan
hal yang tidak sopan ini.</font>

64
00:04:01,770 --> 00:04:05,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini adalah hari dimana aku memberikan
hadiah pernikahan kepada calon istriku.</font>

65
00:04:05,010 --> 00:04:07,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menyuruh tentaramu...</font>

66
00:04:08,210 --> 00:04:10,750
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk melawan
Seja Jeoha...</font>

67
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:11,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau Yang Mulia?</font>

68
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha, mengapa anda---</font>

69
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:15,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau membuatku ragu padamu?</font>

70
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:18,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membuatku khawatir.</font>

71
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:23,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa...</font>

72
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:31,700
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku ingin menghentikan ini.</font>

73
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:34,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika harta Ayahmu menjadi miliknya,</font>

74
00:04:34,670 --> 00:04:36,740
<font color=#FFFF00>...maka itu bisa menimbulkan masalah bagiku.</font>

75
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:40,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau boleh membenciku.</font>

76
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:43,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi aku menyarankan untuk
menjauh dari pria seperti dia.</font>

77
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:11,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia meminta secangkir air,
tapi saat aku kembali,</font>

78
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:12,810
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia sudah pergi.</font>

79
00:05:12,910 --> 00:05:14,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

80
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Setelah aku bertemu mereka pertama kali,</i></font>

81
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:38,570
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...aku seharusnya tidak bertemu mereka lagi.</i></font>

82
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,170
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itulah...</i></font>

83
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:45,580
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...yang dilakukan seseorang
untuk menyembunyikan jati dirinya.</i></font>

84
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:48,880
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Namun,</i></font>

85
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:51,380
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Saat-saat itu membuatku bahagia...</i></font>

86
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:53,280
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan juga terluka.</i></font>

87
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,750
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan aku terjebak disini.</i></font>

88
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan pergi meninggalkan mereka.</i></font>

89
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak apa-apa jika aku bertahan satu hari lagi.</i></font>

90
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,490
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku ingin tetap seperti ini.</i></font>

91
00:06:08,530 --> 00:06:09,930
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sehari lagi.</i></font>

92
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hanya sehari lagi.</i></font>

93
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:29,250
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku bahagia dan dan juga kesakitan.</i></font>

94
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:33,520
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Orang yang selalu
tersenyum padaku...</i></font>

95
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:36,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...menyimpan sesuatu yang menyedihkan,</i></font>

96
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:37,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan itu membuat hatiku sakit.</i></font>

97
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:42,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku seharusnya tidak pernah lahir.</i></font>

98
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:51,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa jatuh, jadi
bersandarlah padaku.</font>

99
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,250
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dan orang yang berada di sampingnya...</i></font>

100
00:06:58,010 --> 00:07:00,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...selalu menghindar untuk menatapku.</i></font>

101
00:07:01,650 --> 00:07:03,190
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Saat aku menatapnya,</i></font>

102
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:07,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dia selalu menghindar.</i></font>

103
00:07:10,290 --> 00:07:11,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dan itu membuat hatiku sakit.</i></font>

104
00:07:16,570 --> 00:07:18,170
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Siapa dari mereka...</i></font>

105
00:07:18,970 --> 00:07:20,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...yang membuat hatiku lebih sakit?</i></font>

106
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa...</font>

107
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:38,120
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau disini?</font>

108
00:07:38,490 --> 00:07:40,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadi berada didekat rumahmu.</font>

109
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku telah...</font>

110
00:07:44,890 --> 00:07:46,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengikutimu dari sana.</font>

111
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:47,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa?</font>

112
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku khawatir.</font>

113
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:52,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut kau akan...</font>

114
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:55,200
<font color=#FFFF00>...tertabrak ketika dijalan...</font>

115
00:07:56,110 --> 00:07:57,240
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau tersandung.</font>

116
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:01,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya tersandung saja.</font>

117
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin melihat
bagaimana reaksimu.</font>

118
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:06,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan bisa
menghentikanmu.</font>

119
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pasti masih jauh.</font>

120
00:08:12,290 --> 00:08:13,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

121
00:08:14,290 --> 00:08:15,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya?</font>

122
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:19,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ternyata Seja Jeoha.</font>

123
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

124
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:27,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia belum
tahu siapa aku.</font>

125
00:08:27,570 --> 00:08:29,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku belum bisa memberitahunya...</font>

126
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...sekarang.</font>

127
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:34,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak tahu siapa aku.</font>

128
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:36,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun dia datang.</font>

129
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:40,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti yang memintanya.</font>

130
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

131
00:08:44,590 --> 00:08:45,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah temanmu.</font>

132
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

133
00:08:49,330 --> 00:08:51,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Teman Seja Jeoha,</font>

134
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:53,960
<font color=#FFFF00>...siapa kau sebenarnya?</font>

135
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku anak Kanselir.</font>

136
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu...</font>

137
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,950
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau Tuan Muda Ketiga?</font>

138
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:10,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

139
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengenalimu dari awal,</font>

140
00:09:13,850 --> 00:09:16,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan bersikap sangat kasar.</font>

141
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana ini?</font>

142
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sudah membohongimu.</font>

143
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:21,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

144
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku minta maaf.</font>

145
00:09:29,730 --> 00:09:32,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah mengucapkan selamat tinggal,
jadi aku akan pergi.</font>

146
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya satu pertanyaan.</font>

147
00:09:48,650 --> 00:09:51,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sejak awal berbicara padaku
dengan sopan.</font>

148
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:55,490
<font color=#FFFF00>...bahkan disaat aku hanya seorang pembantu.</font>

149
00:09:58,530 --> 00:09:59,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa?</font>

150
00:10:00,430 --> 00:10:01,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kau...</font>

151
00:10:03,170 --> 00:10:05,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...wanita yang dicintai Tuanku.</font>

152
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:10,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mencintaimu dari awal bertemu.</font>

153
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa besok saja?</font>

154
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:42,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda harus datang sekarang.</font>

155
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:49,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, aku akan datang sekarang. Aku akan datang.</font>

156
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku membuat kesalahan?</font>

157
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya pulang dengan bangga.</font>

158
00:10:57,690 --> 00:10:59,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu siapa Hong Kyu?</font>

159
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:00,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mempertaruhkan nyawanya...</font>

160
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk melawan dan membunuh
pemberontak demi Ayahku.</font>

161
00:11:03,590 --> 00:11:05,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mempertaruhkan nyawanya...</font>

162
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:07,000
<font color=#FFFF00>...demi aku dan Ayahku.</font>

163
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:09,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mengawalku jika ada kunjungan kenegaraan,</font>

164
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:12,000
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menjaga kamarku semalaman
saat aku kedinginan.</font>

165
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat aku sakit,</font>

166
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:15,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia juga tidak makan.</font>

167
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:18,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah pria terhormat yang memiliki...</font>

168
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,840
<font color=#FFFF00>...banyak kontribusi.</font>

169
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:23,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau mengirim
putrinya sebagai persembahan!</font>

170
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:30,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau melakukan ini?
Kenapa kau membuatku sangat kesal?</font>

171
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:33,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau datang terlambat, Seja.</font>

172
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menunggumu.</font>

173
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:38,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku disini.</font>

174
00:11:42,730 --> 00:11:44,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu?</font>

175
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:47,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dilakukan Ibumu pada Hong Kyu...</font>

176
00:11:47,570 --> 00:11:49,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan putrinya?</font>

177
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:52,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mencambuknya dengan cambuk baja
sehingga dia tidak bisa berjalan,</font>

178
00:11:52,210 --> 00:11:53,480
<font color=#FFFF00>...menyita hartanya,</font>

179
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,240
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan sekarang, dia ingin mengasingkannya.</font>

180
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:58,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sudah tahu.</font>

181
00:11:58,380 --> 00:12:00,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian berdua bekerjasama dengan baik.</font>

182
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:03,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sangat sibuk
melakukan hal yang sama seperti...</font>

183
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:05,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...Ibumu tersayang...</font>

184
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan merusak pernikahan orang lain.</font>

